properties.description: 銷貨與銷退單整合庫存單位、成本資訊

sqlReaderQuery.value: @concat('select * , lower(tH009) th009_L, lower(stock_unit) stock_unit_L, th008+th024 as sales_qty from erp.V_SO_WITH_COST where  YEAR(COALESCE(NULLIF(MODI_DATE, ''''), CREATE_DATE)) >= '  , formatDateTime(addDays(addhours(utcnow(),8),-1),'yyyy'))

@concat('select *, lower(tj008) tj008_L , lower(stock_unit) stock_unit_L, tj007+tj047 as return_qty from erp.V_SO_RETURN_WITH_COST where  YEAR(COALESCE(NULLIF(MODI_DATE, ''''), CREATE_DATE)) >= '  , formatDateTime(addDays(addhours(utcnow(),8),-1),'yyyy'))

activities.name: ConvertQTY_SO
activities.description: 將出貨單位與數量轉換為庫存單位與數量

scripts.text:
update stage.COPTH
set converted_qty = erp.Quantity_conversion(tH004, tH009, sales_qty, stock_unit)
where YEAR(COALESCE(NULLIF(MODI_DATE, ''''), CREATE_DATE)) >= year(getdate() - 1)
